com.zhonghu.sip.api

类 SipProfileState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zhonghu.sip.api.SipProfileState
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SipProfileState
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Holder for a sip profile state.
    It allows to unpack content values from registration/activation status of a SipProfile.
    另请参阅:
